(MUNCHING)

1100
01:04:14,040 --> 01:04:15,799
Come on.

1101
01:04:15,800 --> 01:04:18,119
- What about Michelle?
- Forget about her.

1102
01:04:18,120 --> 01:04:19,759
That girl's only good
for one thing.

1103
01:04:19,760 --> 01:04:21,919
