01:04:50,400 --> 01:04:53,479
Face it, if this was a film
and you saw that,

1113
01:04:53,480 --> 01:04:55,239
what would you be
shouting at the screen?

1114
01:04:55,240 --> 01:04:57,919
Turn around! Go back!

1115
01:04:57,920 --> 01:05:00,885
I know, but we must save Abu.

1116
01:05:01,960 --> 01:05:04,401
(GASPING)

1117
01:05:04,560 --> 01:05:06,250
(HARRY) 'This is it.'

